<el-tabs class="dynamic-tab"
         v-model="activeIndex"
         @tab-remove="handleRemove"
         @tab-click="handleClick"
         type="card">
  <el-tab-pane v-for="item in tabs"
               :key="item.id"
               :label="item.title"
               :labelContent="()=>(item)"
               :name="item.id"
               :closable="item.closable">
  </el-tab-pane>
</el-tabs>
